source.name: CHM@L Market Map
source.description:
CHM@L's GEO club would like to invite ALL students to participate in their project. Help them by collecting data next time you visit your local grocery store, farmer's market, small market, corner market, etc.. 
1) Take a photo at the market
2) Record the price of an apple (any kind, just let us know)
3) Tell Geo Club what you learned by completing this form.
